autiful
  but subtle perfume made from the <span class=3DSpellE>Natarril</span> pla=
nt.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Natarril</span> is a small shru=
b with
  tiny blue-green leaves and dazzling multi-<span class=3DSpellE>color</spa=
n>
  flowers. It is typically found clinging to rocky cliff-faces on Desert
  worlds.</p>
